Sentencas: Composite cathodes Ag-La0.6Sr0.4Co0.2Fe0.8O3-delta were obtained by two different procedures.
Titulo: COMPOSITE Ag-La0.6Sr0.4Co0.8Fe0.2O3-δ CATHODE MATERIAL FOR SOLID OXIDE FUEL CELLS, PREPARATION AND CHARACTERISTIC

Sentencas: In the first procedure porous La0.6Sr0.4Co0.2Fe0.8O3-delta (LSCF) matrix was prepared by sintering the LSCF paste, the matrix was then saturated with AgNO3 solution and sintered again.
Titulo: COMPOSITE Ag-La0.6Sr0.4Co0.8Fe0.2O3-δ CATHODE MATERIAL FOR SOLID OXIDE FUEL CELLS, PREPARATION AND CHARACTERISTIC

Sentencas: Introduced silver crystalized in the form of 10 nm crystallites in the whole LSCF matrix.
Titulo: COMPOSITE Ag-La0.6Sr0.4Co0.8Fe0.2O3-δ CATHODE MATERIAL FOR SOLID OXIDE FUEL CELLS, PREPARATION AND CHARACTERISTIC

Sentencas: In the second procedure the paste of silver powder was deposited on the surface of electrolyte and dried.
Titulo: COMPOSITE Ag-La0.6Sr0.4Co0.8Fe0.2O3-δ CATHODE MATERIAL FOR SOLID OXIDE FUEL CELLS, PREPARATION AND CHARACTERISTIC

Sentencas: The layer of silver paste was then covered by a layer of the LSCF paste and sintered at 850 degrees C.
Titulo: COMPOSITE Ag-La0.6Sr0.4Co0.8Fe0.2O3-δ CATHODE MATERIAL FOR SOLID OXIDE FUEL CELLS, PREPARATION AND CHARACTERISTIC

Sentencas: The following cells were tested: H-2 vertical bar Ni-Ce0.8Gd0.2O1.9 vertical bar Ce0.8Sm0.2O1.9 vertical bar LSCF vertical bar O-2, H-2 vertical bar Ni-Ce0.8Gd0.2O1.9 vertical bar Ce0.8Sm0.2O1.9 vertical bar LSCF-Ag vertical bar O-2 and H-2 vertical bar Ni-Ce0.8Gd0.2O1.9 vertical bar Ce0.8Sm0.2O1.9 vertical bar Ag vertical bar LSCF vertical bar O-2.
Titulo: COMPOSITE Ag-La0.6Sr0.4Co0.8Fe0.2O3-δ CATHODE MATERIAL FOR SOLID OXIDE FUEL CELLS, PREPARATION AND CHARACTERISTIC

Sentencas: Introduction of silver interlayer between cathode and electrolyte increased output power by 18-28% whereas introduction of metallic silver into porous LSCF caused increase in power by 14-18%.
Titulo: COMPOSITE Ag-La0.6Sr0.4Co0.8Fe0.2O3-δ CATHODE MATERIAL FOR SOLID OXIDE FUEL CELLS, PREPARATION AND CHARACTERISTIC
